    <title>Applying student number controls to alternative providers with designated courses: consultation</title>
    <content type="html">&lt;div class="govspeak"&gt;&lt;p&gt;Respond by 23 January 2013. Consultation seeking views from higher education providers on controlling student numbers where they have courses designated for student support purposes. It aims to provide an overview of the new system for alternative providers that wish their students to be able to access student support from the Student Loans Company, to seek responses to specific proposals on student number controls, and to invite views on aspects of how this will operate in practice.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content>
