    <id>tag:www.gov.uk,2005:PublicationesquePresenter/46193</id>
    <published>2012-02-28T00:00:00+00:00</published>
    <updated>2012-02-28T00:00:00+00:00</updated>
    <link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/business-university-collaboration-the-wilson-review"/>
    <title>Business-university collaboration: the Wilson review</title>
    <content type="html">&lt;div class="govspeak"&gt;&lt;p&gt;Independent review for BIS by Dr Tim Wilson, following the Higher education white paper (URN 11/944), which states the need for stronger links to be formed between universities and employers. The review makes recommendations on work and enterprise experience and recruitment for undergraduates and graduates. Other recommendations aim to improve the experience of businesses seeking to collaborate with universities. The review places universities in their wider context locally and internationally, recommending how to strengthen their collaboration with business in this wider context.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content>
